snippet.title: Sniper Ghost Warrior 3 Trailer PS4 XboxOne
snippet.description:
Sniper Ghost Warrior 3 is all that you would want from a sniping game, sit back cover up and get them shots! Who doesn't want to snipe from massive distances.

Subscribe to our channel for more. Check out our other vids and follow us on Twitter @ForTheReplay

For Guides and Walkthroughs check out @ClickToUnlock our sister channel at https://www.youtube.com/user/EscherMedia
